{
  "stem": "21437.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead of 5 to 4:00, we were there earlier-- something-- perhaps something-- now, when I talk about it, it could have had something to do with this, what was going to happen next.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the train went much earlier, and he missed the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said, OK, 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Between 2:00 and 3:00, we heard running of the boots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard a lot of noise-- shouting, shoving, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The beginning of liquidation of the ghetto happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, in the next three days-- [SIGH] --they were all-- I wasn't there with my parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because my father-- straight away, when they took us, they make like a makeshift-- it was in a building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- again, it was not in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was somewhere on the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can see the trees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can see it all, but not, of course, for a long time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'll show you the picture I've got of the liquidation of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father said to me, you go with me now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There's like a little room, like a makeshift hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There are people who are sick on top of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there is-- there was a curtain or under the bed-- this is where you hide.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said to me then, remember, I promise you, whatever-- we won't be separated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whatever will happen to one will happen to the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whatever will be, we will together for always.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Just stay where you are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this is where I was for the next three days-- or under the bed, or behind the-- where it was something like a curtain or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't remember getting any food.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
